ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推介導演沖田修一新作 Band友愛回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無簡介</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cinema.com.hk/cmsimg/cinweb/movie/movie_1479292090.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinema.com.hk%2Fcmsimg%2Fcinweb%2Fmovie%2Fmovie_1479292090.jpg&h=ad083263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《字裡人間》松田龍平今次變身做頹爆band友永吉，因女友由佳(前田敦子 飾)懷孕，只好死死地氣回去闊別7年的鄉下向父母報告。他與父親(柄本明 飾)一向是冤家，二人一見面便大打出手﹗永吉本想快快走人，誰知父親突然倒地，被診斷患上末期癌症。他頓時醒覺父母經已老去，決定留下來幫忙，更絞盡腦汁替父親實現那些奇怪的願望。雖然二人互看不順眼，其實一直都很重視對方。《那年遇上世之介》導演沖田修一幽默滾動力作，兩大影帝松田龍平及柄本明動容演繹父子的微妙關係。電影榮獲烏甸尼遠東電影節評審團大獎及觀眾選擇大獎。"},{"pid":"6702569d21c5b94e453603ce33d4ecabe89b1c5b","tid":145871,"uid":21624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"呢套真係好正<br />\n睇完我都想成為好似世之介咁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d97224cdc6a972a0ac700d906823b78f1abb03d","tid":145871,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得書好睇啲, 電影cut 咗好多details</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下CUT左D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510595b727001d861772396ecd683992da929951","tid":145871,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套真係好正<br />\n睇完我都想成為好似世之介咁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世之介雖然係個小人物,但係每個人諗起佢都會有開心既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888e399a4286e0bc3ac920125b3412f83db37842","tid":145871,"uid":19250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:39:41.000Z","msg":"我覺得好好睇，世之介好pure 好true 啊啊啊"},{"pid":"b0949575daeedaf3e